front.title: •You Cannot Hide Forever (V)
front.gametext: Plays on table. If an 'insert' card was just inserted or revealed, it is canceled. You lose no Force to Boonta Eve Podrace. While you occupy more battlegrounds than opponent, I Did It! is suspended.
front.lore: 'Give yourself to the dark side. It is the only way you can save your friends.'
